text: Okrog pri Motniku () is a small settlement in the Municipality of Kamnik in the Upper Carniola region of Slovenia. ==Name== The name of the settlement was changed from Spodnji Okrog to Okrog pri Motniku in 1955.Spremembe naselij 1948–95. 1996.
